<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.7.6">
<l>pirāṉpe runilaṅ kīṇṭavaṉ piṉṉum</l>
<l>virāyma larttuḻāy vēynta muṭiyaṉ</l>
<l>marāmara meyta māyava ṉeṉṉu</l>
<l>ḷirāṉeṉil piṉṉai yāṉoṭṭu vēṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord, the one who moreover split the great ground,</l>
<l>the one with a crown fragrantly covered by blooming Tulsi,</l>
<l>the trickster who shot the Cadamba trees, if he</l>
<l>is not  in my heart, will I stick to him?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
